-- cartesianProduct :: [a] -> [b] -> [(a, b)]
on cartesianProduct(xs, ys)
    script
        on |位|(x)
            script
                on |位|(y)
                    {Tuple(x, y)}
                end |位|
            end script
            concatMap(result, ys)
        end |位|
    end script
    concatMap(result, xs)
end cartesianProduct
